      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Thou hast seen, O Lord — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "As they say they have seen, so my comfort is, that thou also hast seen, and dost observe all their plots and threats, and all my distresses and calamities, which I suffer for thy sake. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
