    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This thou hast seen, O Lord,.... The insults and derisions of these men, and the injuries they did to him, whom they hated. God is omniscient, and sees all things, all the evil wicked men do to him; and he will requite them in his own time; see ",
        "children": []
